Package: riva
Type: Package
Title: Rare biosphere and indicator species visualization and analysis.
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-02-17
Authors@R: person("Michael", "Lynch", email = "mdjlynch@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of functions useful for exploring (visualization) and analysis of
  rare biosphere and indicator species dynamics in microbial ecosystems. The name riva
  (Rare biosphere and Indicator Visualization and Analysis) also alludes to the "entangled bank"
  in the final paragraph of Origin of Species (riva = bank or shore in Italian)
Depends: biom, ggplot
License: GPL (>=2)
